# Render production URLs (set these in Render dashboard for each service)
# Frontend (web):  https://re-sourcing-web.onrender.com/
# Backend (API):  https://re-sourcing-api.onrender.com/
#
# Web service env:  NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://re-sourcing-api.onrender.com
# API service env: CORS_ORIGIN=https://re-sourcing-web.onrender.com
#
# Optional: NYC Geoclient (address → BBL/BIN). Get key at https://api-portal.nyc.gov (geoclient-current-v2).
# GEOCLIENT_SUBSCRIPTION_KEY=
#
# Optional: NYC Open Data app token (better rate limits for Socrata enrichment).
# SOCRATA_APP_TOKEN=
